N> in <LOCATION> Lorman </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Miss. </LOCATION>, and at <ORGANIZATION> Mississippi </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> State </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> University </ORGANIZATION> at <LOCATION> Starkville </LOCATION> on the same day.
