<HEAD>South Korean Minister Says U.S. Pressure Could Spark Instability</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Korea</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By SUSANNE M. SCHAFER</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
