<SECOND>AM-Bush-Tennis,220</SECOND>
<HEAD>Bush Takes Time Out to Play Tennis with Bjorn Borg and Swedes.</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
