 Here are sample questions from integrity and substance-abuse tests, designed and marketed by Las Vegas-based <ORGANIZATION> Lousig-Nont </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> & </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> amp </ORGANIZATION><ORGANIZATION> ; </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associates </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Inc. </ORGANIZATION>:
